name: VMF
description: The new VMF LED Series offers clean, functional styling that is defined by its sleek low profile design and rugged construction. It combines LED performance and advanced LED thermal management technology and provides outdoor lighting that is both energy efficient and aesthetically pleasing. The LED’s performance and the driver’s life are maximized by enclosing them in two separate cast aluminum housings. The LED light assemblies come with 48 to 96 LED’s. Four optical distribution patterns are available. Choose between 3000, 4000 or 5000 Kelvin temperature of the LEDs. A durable polyester powder coat finish is guaranteed for five years; and is available in standard or custom colors.

name: V-Arch Bollard
description: V-Bollard – part of our V-Collection is a high performance architectural LED luminaire to be used in outdoor lighting applications. Sleek design takes advantage of the low profile LED lamp technology. Superior thermal management allows for maximum LPW output.
